name: #2 POSTCAD FROM BARCELONA (front)
description:
This is a postcard from a place where I spent more than 6 months walking the street until I lose myself meeting the city.

Was a special place to me, where I could speak my mother language and where I really start to work hard to earn money to go to India.

Barcelona, a place where you can be whoever you want to be. The city where everybody haves a place to be and blossom. 

I was a solo walking photographer founding myself on the lonely street.
Was hard that loneliness but my story makes me went there to understood why I was traveling so much for long years.
